title: 46. "Oh I am Jealous" Working Through Jealousy
description:
Hey girl!

In this episode, we talk about jealousy. Where does jealousy come from? What is the root of jealousy? How do you move past jealousy? How do you work through jealousy? We address all this and more in this week's episode, you don't want to miss it!

Please don't forget to rate & review!
